<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>靈性 on Lucky Stone</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7/</link><description>Recent content in 靈性 on Lucky Stone</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>紫水晶 x 眉心輪 &amp; 頂輪：一顆石頭，同時打開兩個靈性能量中心</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E8%BC%AA%E8%88%87%E9%A0%82%E8%BC%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E8%BC%AA%E8%88%87%E9%A0%82%E8%BC%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;大多數水晶只對應一個脈輪。紫水晶不一樣——它同時連結眉心輪和頂輪，也就是七脈輪體系裡最頂端的兩個能量中心。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶功效完整解析：靈性修行入門首選</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A5%E9%96%80%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A5%E9%96%80%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;在水晶店走了一圈，最後手裡還是捧著一顆紫水晶——你不孤單，幾乎每個人的起點都在這裡。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>